project_descr: Support to Sustainable  Energy for All Initiative

outputs.output_descr: The majority of Sub-Saharan African countries are faced today with the challenge of meeting the Millennium Development Goals (MDG) by 2015 and the objectives of access to sustainable energy as defined in the UN initiative «Sustainable Energy for All». Whatever the going trend is, it is acknowledged that poor access to sustainable and modern energy services is a major shortcoming to economic and social development.
